org.javaavc.ffmpeg.avformat

Interface LibavformatLibrary.AVStreamParseType

  • Enclosing interface:
    LibavformatLibrary

    public static interface LibavformatLibrary.AVStreamParseType
    enum values

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int AVSTREAM_PARSE_FULL
      < full parsing and repack
      static int AVSTREAM_PARSE_FULL_ONCE
      < full parsing and repack of the first frame only, only implemented for H.264 currently
      static int AVSTREAM_PARSE_FULL_RAW
      < full parsing and repack with timestamp and position generation by parser for raw
      this assumes that each packet in the file contains no demuxer level headers and
      just codec level data, otherwise position generation would fail
      static int AVSTREAM_PARSE_HEADERS
      < Only parse headers, do not repack.
      static int AVSTREAM_PARSE_NONE 
      static int AVSTREAM_PARSE_TIMESTAMPS
      < full parsing and interpolation of timestamps for frames not starting on a packet boundary
